**      OpenCL binding (and more) for Scala
**
**         http://www.hsyl20.fr/auratune
**
*/

This project aims at providing an efficient binding between Scala and OpenCL.


Build instructions:
------------------

This project uses SBT (simple build tool).

Developers:
----------
Sylvain HENRY - sylvain.henry@inria.fr


Packages:
--------

fr.hsyl20.opencl - OpenCL binding (using SNA and JNA)
fr.hsyl20.auratune.runtime - Runtime system
fr.hsyl20.auratune.runtime.schedulers - Available schedulers for the runtime system
fr.hsyl20.auratune.runtime.opencl - OpenCL backend for the runtime system

